    "status": "generated",
    "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p><b>Hospitalization:</b> Admission via ER for fever, cough, and dyspnea.</p><p>Child encounters represent ER care, internal ward A stay, and a PICC line procedure performed during the ward stay.</p><p>Admission and comorbidity diagnoses are recorded as encounter diagnoses, while the detailed clinical data is stored in referenced Condition resources.</p></div>"
